<br />\n  雙方管理層立即向前線同事了解事件，明白到同事在如此混亂的情況下工作，承受很大的壓力，管理層對出現上述情況表示明白及理解。<br />\n<br />\n  事發後，消防處和警方的高級管理層、指揮層級及前線同事已立即溝通，加強互相了解，而事件已得到妥善處理。兩部門必定會繼續加強對前線同事的指引及支援協助，避免再有不愉快事件發生。<br />\n<br />\n  因應持續出現的非法及暴力事件，警務處及消防處的人員有需要繼續在現場執行艱巨任務。雙方會繼續互相體諒、支持和合作，期望盡快令社會回復穩定。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年11月9日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間20時10分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/09/P2019110900733.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201911%2F09%2FP2019110900733.htm&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=80cfe975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201911/09/P2019110900733.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:15:56.000Z","msg":"人地都不割 你睇下我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d959e86043a4cf4d37ffe253bb3b43a22da3f76e","tid":1701982,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:17:36.000Z","msg":"救護員比曱甴叫垃圾都要硬食"},{"pid":"579f3b189984c82aa9ac46a066851830bfd86cfa","tid":1701982,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:20:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"52b4c8f75277cf23976a093c739146672799a5d5","tid":1701982,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11335b14b78af30e9acdb2f11f95c157f640b7da","tid":1701982,"uid":84116,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"89675d0b43a43c2967042ff94995ad07f63235e3","tid":1701982,"uid":240362,"like":77,"dislike":2,"score":75,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:42:02.000Z","msg":"又要救護員硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"消防散仔都唔照呀，仲點會照救護散仔<img src=\"/asset